OL,3,CP&O Ferries boss admits he couldn't
OL,4,Clive on seafarer wage in grilling by
OL,5,CMPs
OL,7,FWatch: P&O Boss Peter Hebblethwaite is
OL,8,Fasked at a committee of cross-party
OL,9,FMPs if he could live on the wage being
OL,10,Fpaid to his seafarers
OL,12,FThe boss of P&O Ferries has told MPs
OL,13,Fthe sudden mass-sacking of almost 800
OL,14,Fworkers is a difficult decision he
OL,15,Fwished the company 'never ever had to
OL,16,Fmake'.
OL,18,FPeter Hebblethwaite faced a grilling
OL,19,Ffrom a cross-party committee and was
OL,20,Fasked 'are you a modern day pirate?'
