OL,7,FLabour MP Liam Byrne, Chair of the
OL,8,FBusiness and Trade Committee,
OL,9,Fpresented evidence which suggested a
OL,10,Fcook on the Dover to Calais route was
OL,11,Fbeing paid #2.90 per hour.
OL,13,FMr Hebblethwaite said "We are paying
OL,14,Fconsiderably ahead of the
OL,15,Finternational minimum standard.
OL,17,F"We believe that it is right, as an
OL,18,Finternational business operating in
OL,19,Finternational waters, we should be
OL,20,Fgoverned by international law."
