OL,7,FChanges to French international law
OL,8,Fmeans the minimum wage will jump to
OL,9,Faround #9 an hour and seafarers won't
OL,10,Fbe allowed to work more than 14
OL,11,Fconsecutive days at a time.
OL,13,FAsked whether P&O will comply,
OL,14,FHebblethwaite told the hearing "yes,
OL,15,Fof course we will".
OL,17,F"These are international seafarers in
OL,18,Finternational waters and we pay ahead
OL,19,Fof the national industry standard"
